08:17.765 --> 08:22.402
What's that?
I'm missing the fireworks!

08:22.470 --> 08:26.540
It's past midnight! How did I get
so sucked into this show again?

08:26.541 --> 08:30.610
It's like everything else
just disappears!

08:30.678 --> 08:32.779
Whoa, whoa.
Don't go.

08:32.847 --> 08:35.748
We're having a really good time!
Here. Look.

08:35.816 --> 08:38.684
I've got the 2-part Hawaii special.

08:38.751 --> 08:42.121
But Steven really wanted
me to do New Year's.

08:42.188 --> 08:44.390
He'll be fine.
He's Steven.

08:44.492 --> 08:46.526
- He's tough.
- I wanted to be there!

08:46.594 --> 08:48.761
Here. Here.
It would have been like this.

08:48.863 --> 08:51.764
Whoa! Fireworks!

08:51.832 --> 08:54.367
Hey, Dad, come on!
Now let's watch

08:54.435 --> 08:57.303
- some "Li'l Butler"!
- Amethyst, you know how I feel

08:57.371 --> 09:00.340
- about shapeshifting.
- Geez. Sorry.

09:00.407 --> 09:02.675
I was just trying to cheer you up.

09:02.743 --> 09:07.583
Oh, that's right ... I forgot.
You're so sensitive.

09:07.618 --> 09:10.693
I know you like making me
uncomfortable, but it's not funny.

09:10.728 --> 09:12.352
I can't stay here and humor you.

09:12.419 --> 09:17.631
- I have to be there for my son.
- Well, what about me, huh?

09:17.666 --> 09:20.654
I had someone who was
always there for me

09:20.655 --> 09:22.295
until she started hanging out with you!

09:22.396 --> 09:24.497
Don't do this, Amethyst ...
seriously.

09:24.598 --> 09:27.100
I bet you'd stay for her.

09:27.167 --> 09:30.666
- You wouldn't.
- What? Do this?

09:30.701 --> 09:33.673
<i>- Where are you going after Hawaii?
- Hey, Greg</i>

09:33.741 --> 09:37.343
<i>Turn around.
Check it out!</i>

09:37.411 --> 09:40.613
I know you're doing it!
I want to be friends again.

09:40.681 --> 09:43.383
I really do.
But I can't let you do this

09:43.450 --> 09:45.718
- to me again!
- Stop!

09:50.891 --> 09:53.026
What are you two doing?!

09:55.195 --> 09:57.597
I get it.
It's hard to deal with stuff

09:57.665 --> 10:00.567
from the past.
You want to put it off because

10:00.668 --> 10:03.797
there's tons of it
and it's really heavy and it means

10:03.804 --> 10:06.482
a lot to you,
so it's hard to let anything go.

10:06.548 --> 10:10.109
But you got to,
because this thing is full!

10:10.177 --> 10:13.680
Seriously, when did
you even have a cat?!

10:23.556 --> 10:26.392
Okay.
We're finishing this today.

10:26.460 --> 10:29.736
Right.
What? Pearl?

10:29.771 --> 10:33.140
Hello, Greg.
Nice of you to join us.

10:33.175 --> 10:35.401
- I don't believe it!
- Whoa!

10:35.502 --> 10:40.239
- I'm so sorry about the mess.
- Was this... your idea?

10:40.307 --> 10:42.520
- Well...
- It was Amethyst's idea.

10:45.911 --> 10:47.580
I-I just thought we

10:47.648 --> 10:49.716
could take all this
stuff back to the temple.

10:49.783 --> 10:52.151
It can fit in my room.
That way, you don't have

10:52.252 --> 10:57.066
to throw anything away.
But ... But you can keep this.

11:00.461 --> 11:04.196
Uh... thank you, Amethyst.

